name: I Know All Negative Effects of Entries in Instances
summary: The world has changed, and instances have descended. One can obtain Extraordinary Power within these instances by using different entries.However, the entries could also bring some negative effects. Luckily, Zhou Yingtian discovers that he seems able to see hints on how to deal with the negative effects of the entries by pairing them appropriately.
